
HOW TO
* check uinput kernel module (/dev/uinput | /dev/input/uinput)
* chown <user> /dev/uinput 
* start MouseMover application to receive json data
 * https://github.com/0xCA5A/kickstart/blob/master/ni_mouse/MouseMover/JSONAnalyzer.cpp
* start a client application (simple_client | kinect | msp430) to send JSON position data and move mouse pointer and send click events



